izing excessive extraction are noted as crucial for quality sparkling wine production.\n\n**Image Description:**\n- Caption: \"Fermentation vessels used to make tank method sparkling wines.\"\n- Image showcases large stainless steel tanks, likely used for the first fermentation stage in sparkling wine production following the traditional method."
